<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good evening Rafae=
lla,</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt; font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,=
sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for taki=
ng the time to meet with me last week.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt=
; font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As discussed, plea=
se find attached a process document which outlines the framework of how Towe=
r Insurance will progress your claim.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;=
 font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">This is a framewor=
k only and the process will change, as we move through each step, given that=
 findings and results will affect the next step in the process. This will be=
 a live document that will gather
 detail as we progress.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt; font-family:&=
quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">However, I do trus=
t that this will give you some insight and knowledge to allow us to particip=
ate in the process together.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt; font-fam=
ily:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to s=
peaking with you soon.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt; font-family:&q=
uot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please confirm bac=
